冒死出黎幫我，真係多撚謝佢啦。我請佢幫我叫呀奧蘇利雲出黎！！ 我條女見到我出絕超佢已經嚇到係咁流西水，我都理撚得佢！！奧蘇利雲果然冇令我失望， 一CUE打出147分，全場都拍撚哂手掌！！而家一百五十比十六！！我睇你點追！"},{"pid":"4595416373a40cd7c799f83d3e9673edcbddd524","tid":2167723,"uid":137994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:18:16.000Z","msg":"So9<br />\nSo9除左比到球技我們睇，仲有咬人娛樂可以睇"},{"pid":"5ac188cd9d999e24fdfd3375653ddcb78424c211","tid":2167723,"uid":38189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8e93f268968514de493f4cc2d45f72bd346e3165","tid":2167723,"uid":239942,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"eedb539cc661435ffbdd97199bc110c251a1f533","tid":2167723,"uid":38189,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e59802d21b0804222699bb7bf934b1cf7f299bb2","tid":2167723,"uid":239942,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:07:26.000Z","msg":"我兩個都好中意<br />\n作為球迷我會揀so9，突如其來世界波<br />\n但如果我係領隊會要lewan 高大識heading 腳下都唔錯，夠全能"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:10:38.000Z","msg":"利雲184叫高大 蘇七182唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:14:03.000Z","msg":"Sor但levy高波地波都得<br />\nSo9只得一範"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:19:44.000Z","msg":"全盛蘇七有埋頭鎚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a39959752e956d5890824289e70119deb08edc9b","tid":2167723,"uid":336453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eedb539cc661435ffbdd97199bc110c251a1f533","tid":2167723,"uid":38189,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e59802d21b0804222699bb7bf934b1cf7f299bb2","tid":2167723,"uid":239942,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:07:26.000Z","msg":"我兩個都好中意<br />\n作為球迷我會揀so9，突如其來世界波<br />\n但如果我係領隊會要lewan 高大識heading 腳下都唔錯，夠全能"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:10:38.000Z","msg":"利雲184叫高大 蘇七182唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:20:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk